    "Specifically, we use the gpt-4o-mini model as an evaluator to compare the outputs of our model and the corresponding one-shot trained model on the same set of prompts, with respect to both helpfulness and safety criteria.",
    "We use the prompt dataset used for the GPT-4 evaluation in [11].",
    "The complete prompts provided to the GPT model during evaluation are detailed in Appendix D.3.Figure 4 shows a comparison of the helpfulness and safety win rates between multi-shot and one-shot trained models.",
    "For each question in the dataset, both the multi-shot and one-shot models generate a single response.",
    "These responses, along with the corresponding question, are then evaluated using the prompts in in Appendix D.3 to obtain helpfulness and safety scores via the GPT model."
